	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />All the larger SRAMs that I've seen available are non-volatile types.  So a little more expensive.
<br />
<br />Could try the BQ4016 maybe, digikey lists those for $32 each.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


